  "description": "<i>Matsumoto T?ru no Kabushiki Hissh?gaku</i> is a stock trading simulation game for which <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?developer=T%c5%8dru+Matsumoto\">T?ru Matsumoto</a>, a famous Japanese business analyst and writer of books about stock markets lent his name. The goal of the game is to increase your starting money of 1 million yen to a total of 100 million yen in a time span of two years. You have a limited amount of actions per day in which you can buy/sell stocks, buy information from several sources like newspapers or consulting charts. Every action as well as time itself decreases personal energy, which can be filled up again by doing leisure activities.",
